# Woad Raider / Woad Warrior
- More cave man than actual human.  They communicate via grunts more often then spoken language. 
  The woad raider's people have existed since before the first Great Ice.
- Can enter berserker rage.
- Class mechanic, woad raiders employ various tattoos across their bodies. Granting different abilities,
  attacks and forms of damage output.

# Spells
  - Basic face tattoo.  Increases damage a certain amount.
